title: The Quest 2 Just Got MORE POWERFUL with a FREE UPGRADE!
description:
Hello and welcome to TUESDAY NEWSDAY! Your number one resource for the entire week's worth of VR news! Today we have a BUNCH of exciting VR topics to cover, from the newest announcement about the Somnium One, a crazy VR headset that i'm getting pretty excited for (And the rest that's going to be at CES), The Oculus Bug Catcher Program, the Quest 2 receiving a pretty awesome performance upgrade, new Ready Player One style Locomotion VR shoes, and SO MUCH MORE! We have a good week of news and I hope you enjoyed!
